      "content": "i cant even sleep anymore. i just keep looking at the news and every single thing is just... death. the oceans, the fires, the extinction. it feels like we are all just walking ghosts in a world that’s already dead. how am i even supposed to care about a \"future\" that isnt even going to happen? it feels so pointless to even exist in this.",
